quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  114,1,"Say: I seek refuge in the Lord of the mankind"
  114,2,the King of mankind
  114,3,the real God of mankind
  114,4,from the mischief of the slinking whisperers (Satan and his workers)
  114,5,who whisper into the hearts of people
  114,6,from among the jinn or from the mankind